        <div class="priority">
          <h4>Economic Growth</h4>
          <p>Activate Community Improvement Districts (CIDs) and a Stonecrest industrial corridor for quality jobs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="priority">
          <h4>Open Government</h4>
          <p>Launch a Transparency Center with real‑time dashboards, Budget 101, and easy public‑records access.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="priority">
          <h4>Partnerships</h4>
          <p>Deepen collaboration with Arabia Mountain, Flat Rock, DeKalb County, local chambers, and sister cities.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="priority">
          <h4>Seniors First</h4>
          <p>More resources, training, and transportation options for our elders.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="priority">
          <h4>Youth & Schools</h4>
